"                             Import Key to YubiKey                              "
"This will import a GPG key from your keyring to the YubiKey.                    "
"Prerequisites:  B2C3D4E5F6A7B8C9 ...                                            "
"  - You must have a GPG key already generated                                   "
"  - The key must be in your GPG keyring                                         "
"Touch Policies:                                                                 "
"No GPG keys found in keyring.                                                   "
"Generate a key first, or import one with: gpg --import <file>                   "
"  Tab  Focus i Ctrl+P  Palette                                                  "
"  Attestation:    Off                                                           "
"                                                                                "
"  g  Generate Key on Card                                                       "
"  i  Import Existing Key                                                        "
"  v  View Full Key Details                                                      "
"  e  Export SSH Public Key                                                      "
"  k  Key Attributes                                                             "
"  t  Touch Policy                                                               "
"  a  Attestation                                                                "
"  Tab  Focus   Ctrl+P  Palette                                                  "
"                                                                                "
"                                                                                "
"                                                                                "
"                                                                                "
"                                                                                "
